milestones.description: Gary Kirsten and Mike Rindel's 190-run partnership is SA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 151 between Wessels and Andrew Hudson
South Africa's 158-run win against Pakistan is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 124-run win against Sri Lanka
Gary Kirsten and Mike Rindel's 190-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 151 between Andrew Hudson and Wessels
Richardson has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (5) in ODIs for SA, going past Richardson's 4
